===================================
 Bioconductor 1.9 Release Schedule
===================================

01 September
============

  * No new packages added to release roster.


05 September
============

**R**:

  * Grand feature freeze for R-2.4.0. Alpha versions available daily.

  * Begin daily building of R-2.4.0 for nightly build and recommend
    same for all project developers.


08 September
============

* Use R-2.4.0 to test your packages.

* First release candidate of annotation packages built and posted to
  devel annotation data repository

* Nightly build switches to the R-2-4-patches branch.


19 September
============

**R**:

  * Beta release of R-2.4.0 available.


25 September
============

**Bioc**:

  * Stage I Code Freeze: no API changes, no new features.

  * Deadline for packages passing R CMD check without error.


29 September
============

**Bioc**:

  * Deadline for packages passing R CMD check without warning.

  * Stage II Code Freeze.  We will be building release repositories
    and testing. *Only* "show-stopper" bugs will be fixed where
    show-stopper is defined by the release team (not package
    maintainer).

  * Annotation data packages finalized.


03 October
==========

**R**:

  * R 2.4.0 is released

**Bioc**:

  * Build final release repositories

  * Testing install scripts, GUI installation


04 October
==========

* Release of Bioconductor 1.9


